snippet.title: Tako no Himitsu: Ocean of Secrets - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Tako no Himitsu: Ocean of Secrets is coming to Kickstarter! Be notified when it’s live: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1373467035/tako-no-himitsu-ocean-of-secrets

From the developers of Save me Mr Tako comes Tako no Himitsu: Ocean of Secrets, a new ARPG set in a world consumed by the shadows of its past. Join six heroes and embark on an adventure to try and save it!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2357380/Tako_no_Himitsu_Ocean_of_Secrets/

A game by Christophe Galati
Graphics: Pixel Boy & Challenger.AAA
Music: Marc-Antoine Archier
Character Design: Valentin Seiche
